title: BRIEF-Frasers Logistics & Industrial Trust Says ‍DPU Of 1.80 Singapore Cents For 1QFY18​
text:

* ‍DPU OF 1.80 SINGAPORE CENTS FOR 1QFY18​ * ‍QTRLY REVENUE A$42.4 MILLION VERSUS A$39.7 MILLION​ * QTRLY ‍ADJUSTED NET PROPERTY INCOME A$33.4 MILLION VERSUS A$30.7 MILLION ​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
